content:
With time sheets priming, you can prime up to three time sheet list views that mobile workers can access and edit offline. This feature is available in the Field Service mobile app for Android and iOS.

From Setup, enter and select Field Service Mobile App Builder. Under App Navigation, select up to three filters for the Time Sheets tab to ensure the time sheets in those list views are primed for offline use.
title: Improving Field Service Efficiency with Time Sheets Priming
